08:31.923 --> 08:33.557
Hi. Uh, Noah.

08:33.591 --> 08:35.692
- Bay: Very funny.
- (Chuckles)

08:35.726 --> 08:38.628
Are you ready for the A.S.L. test?

08:38.663 --> 08:40.830
Uh, yes. You?

08:40.865 --> 08:44.467
I think I understand everything.

08:44.502 --> 08:47.370
Mm, except for "understand."

08:47.405 --> 08:48.772
This is "understand."

08:48.806 --> 08:50.640
You signed "horny."

08:50.675 --> 08:53.376
Mm. Crap.

08:53.411 --> 08:55.012
I haven't gotten one full sentence right.

08:56.581 --> 08:59.416
Great, what do you think they've cut now?

09:01.452 --> 09:02.485
Hey, what's going on?

09:02.486 --> 09:05.190
_

09:05.191 --> 09:08.630
_

09:09.093 --> 09:10.260
"Student tolerance retreat this weekend.

09:10.294 --> 09:12.162
- Attendance mandatory."
- (Bay sighs)

09:12.196 --> 09:13.356
I'm guessing I'm on the list.

09:13.364 --> 09:15.198
Bet I am too.

09:15.233 --> 09:17.802
I'm guessing so is she.

09:17.803 --> 09:19.315
_

09:25.676 --> 09:26.843
Thanks.

09:32.650 --> 09:33.583
"Crybaby."

09:35.454 --> 09:38.533
_

09:53.365 --> 09:55.366
So it's all of the pilot program kids

09:55.400 --> 09:57.902
and some of the deaf kids?

09:57.936 --> 09:59.136
Yup.

09:59.171 --> 10:01.205
At a tolerance retreat?

10:01.240 --> 10:02.840
Mm-hmm.

10:02.875 --> 10:04.809
But there isn't a problem?

10:13.519 --> 10:15.586
Okay, maybe there were
a few misunderstandings.

10:15.621 --> 10:18.623
But that's just because the
whole thing is new to everyone.

10:18.657 --> 10:21.792
Bay, I know you feel like you have to
make it sound like everything is fine

10:21.827 --> 10:23.461
because you pushed so hard, but...

10:23.495 --> 10:25.329
Mom, everything is fine.

10:25.364 --> 10:27.265
And I promise if I need you guys,

10:27.299 --> 10:29.367
I will tell you, okay?

10:29.401 --> 10:31.235
<i>- Okay.
- Okay.</i>

10:31.270 --> 10:32.303
Have fun.

10:32.337 --> 10:35.406
<i>(Door opens and closes)</i>

10:35.440 --> 10:37.208
I knew this school wasn't a good idea.

10:43.015 --> 10:44.081
At Buckner,

10:44.116 --> 10:46.784
when there were problems
with groups of kids,

10:46.818 --> 10:49.059
we would have assemblies...
we'd do trust falls in the gym

10:49.087 --> 10:51.722
or pass around like a talking stick.

10:51.757 --> 10:54.859
We were not sent into the woods
to reenact "The Hunger Games."

10:54.893 --> 10:56.694
Maybe you should have thought about that

10:56.728 --> 10:59.263
before you hit Natalie with a volleyball.

10:59.298 --> 11:01.432
(Scoffs) I apologized for that.

11:01.466 --> 11:04.268
And then she was the
one who bombed my locker.

11:04.303 --> 11:07.371
Oh, so you're just an
innocent victim in all of this.

11:07.406 --> 11:10.107
I told I was sorry you
and the leadership kids

11:10.142 --> 11:13.177
got dragged into this,
but maybe if you weren't

11:13.211 --> 11:15.212
such an upstanding student...

11:15.247 --> 11:18.082
Wait, now it's my fault that I
have to spend my weekend doing this?

11:18.116 --> 11:20.117
No, I'm just saying it's not my fault.

11:20.152 --> 11:21.752
Okay, I was supposed to bring my mom

11:21.787 --> 11:22.954
to the spa this weekend,

11:22.988 --> 11:25.623
because she was feeling
so bad about Angelo

11:25.657 --> 11:26.991
and his new baby.

11:27.025 --> 11:30.461
Something that you didn't
bother telling me about.

11:30.495 --> 11:31.596
Why didn't you tell me?

11:32.698 --> 11:34.465
I should have, I know.

11:34.499 --> 11:37.635
But when I found out, Regina didn't know.

11:37.669 --> 11:42.173
And then Angelo and I
got into this big fight.

11:42.207 --> 11:43.507
I'm sorry.

11:43.542 --> 11:45.443
I have to go get the rest of my stuff.

11:48.981 --> 11:50.948
(Sighs)

11:52.017 --> 11:54.885
Okay, I guess I'm ready to go.

11:54.920 --> 11:56.187
Try not to be too mad at Bay.

11:56.221 --> 11:58.990
I'm sure she feels bad
about all of this too.

11:59.024 --> 12:00.791
I know. I just...

12:00.826 --> 12:02.793
I was really looking forward
to spending time with you.

12:02.828 --> 12:03.928
Me too.

12:03.962 --> 12:06.897
(Sighs) But we can just do next weekend.

12:06.932 --> 12:09.900
And while you're gone I can
catch up on "Breaking Bad"

12:09.935 --> 12:12.770
and count the amount of times
grandma says "I told you so."

12:12.804 --> 12:14.572
Hey.

12:14.606 --> 12:16.440
Why don't you come with us?

12:16.475 --> 12:18.476
- On the retreat?
- Yeah.

12:18.510 --> 12:19.510
Why not?

12:19.544 --> 12:21.078
You can hang out with Melody,

12:21.113 --> 12:22.246
eat s'mores,

12:22.280 --> 12:23.981
avoid grandma.

12:24.016 --> 12:25.383
I do make a mean s'more.

12:25.417 --> 12:27.051
You really do.

12:28.286 --> 12:30.755
You know what? I think
that's a great idea.

12:30.789 --> 12:31.889
I have a doctor's
appointment in the afternoon,

12:31.923 --> 12:33.004
but I can meet you up there.

12:33.025 --> 12:34.825
Are you having more
problems with your hands?

12:34.860 --> 12:36.961
Actually, no.

12:36.995 --> 12:39.864
Um, this is somebody new
and she's run lots of tests

12:39.898 --> 12:42.633
and seems optimistic.
I'm hoping for good news.

12:42.668 --> 12:44.735
- That's so great!
- I know.

12:44.770 --> 12:45.770
Come as soon as you can.

12:45.804 --> 12:47.505
Okay.

12:48.539 --> 12:51.208
<i>Lana: And you didn't
know two weeks ago that</i>

12:51.243 --> 12:52.510
the parts needed to come from Germany?

12:52.544 --> 12:54.245
We hoped we could get them locally.

12:54.279 --> 12:56.347
Well, my insurance won't
cover any more rental car days.

12:56.381 --> 12:57.481
I'm really sorry.

12:57.516 --> 13:00.084
I am a pregnant woman walking eight blocks

13:00.118 --> 13:01.986
to and from the bus stop every day.

13:02.020 --> 13:03.087
My wife has had four kids.

13:03.121 --> 13:05.222
She says exercise is
good for you and the baby.

13:05.257 --> 13:07.024
Helps with the delivery.

13:07.059 --> 13:09.060
Oh, really? Dr. Larry.

13:09.094 --> 13:10.995
Is there any other medical
advice you would like

13:11.029 --> 13:12.830
to give me or my unborn child?

13:12.864 --> 13:15.066
- Hi.
- We are not done here.

13:15.100 --> 13:16.767
No, sorry. Um...

13:16.802 --> 13:19.603
- Don't know if you remember me, but...
- Yeah.

13:19.638 --> 13:21.439
From Angelo's place.

13:21.473 --> 13:23.501
Right. Yeah. Can I help?

13:23.502 --> 13:24.769
I swear her car will be ready tomorrow.

13:24.803 --> 13:26.570
Well, mine's done now. I could give you

13:26.605 --> 13:29.540
a ride home today and bring you
back tomorrow, if that would help.

13:29.574 --> 13:30.508
Tomorrow.

13:30.542 --> 13:32.410
As God as my witness.

13:35.480 --> 13:38.983
Um, okay, I... I really
don't wanna put you out.

13:39.017 --> 13:41.085
You're not.

13:41.119 --> 13:42.119
Okay. Thanks.

13:42.154 --> 13:43.087
Sure.

